oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Women on cliff
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three women on Bee Rock, Monterey, Tennessee. Two of the women, wearing a dress with belt and a skirt, with collared shirt and cardigan stand, while another woman is seated, in white dress, with legs hanging of the edge of the rock.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
